@startuml UC-004: Submit Lab for Grading

title UC-004: Submit Lab for Grading
autonumber

actor Student
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Submission API\n(Elysia)" as API
participant "GNS3Service" as GNS3Service
participant "IPGenerator" as IPGenerator
participant "SubmissionService" as SubmissionService
database "MongoDB" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ" as RMQ
participant "Grading Service\n(FastAPI)" as Grader
participant "MinIO" as MinIO
participant "Devices\n(GNS3)" as Devices

== Submission Flow ==
Student -> Client: Submit lab answers
Client -> API: POST /v0/submissions\n(with project_id)

API -> API: Verify authentication (JWT)
API -> DB: Validate Lab & Part (Check Deadlines/Prereqs)

opt If project_id is provided
    API -> GNS3Service: getProjectNodes(projectId)
    GNS3Service -> GNS3Service: Fetch assigned GNS3 Server config
    GNS3Service --> API: Return Node List (Name, Console Port, Status)
end

API -> IPGenerator: generateJobFromLab(..., gns3Nodes)

IPGenerator -> IPGenerator: Generate IPs (Management + VLANs)
IPGenerator -> IPGenerator: Map Device Names to GNS3 Console Ports
IPGenerator -> IPGenerator: Build Job Payload (Task ID, Template Name, Params)

API -> SubmissionService: createSubmission(status: pending)
SubmissionService -> DB: Insert Submission Record

API -> RMQ: Publish Grading Job
RMQ --> API: Job Queued

API --> Client: 200 OK + jobId
Client --> Student: Grading in progress...

== Async Grading Execution ==
note over RMQ, Grader: Grading Execution (Async)

RMQ -> Grader: Consume Job

loop For each Task in Job
    Grader -> MinIO: Fetch Custom Task Template (YAML)
    MinIO --> Grader: Return YAML Content
    Grader -> Grader: Parse Template & Prepare Nornir Task
end

loop For each device in job
    Grader -> Devices: Connect via Console Port / SSH
    Devices --> Grader: Connection Established
    Grader -> Devices: Execute Commands (from Task Template)
    Devices --> Grader: Command Output
end

Grader -> Grader: Validate Outputs against Expected Regex/Values
Grader -> Grader: Calculate Final Score

== Result Processing ==
Grader -> API: POST /v0/submissions/result
API -> SubmissionService: storeGradingResult()
SubmissionService -> DB: Update Submission (status: completed/failed)

SubmissionService --> API: Result Stored
API --> Grader: 200 OK

@enduml
